data.name: Amulet of Ambition
data.desc: Equip only to a Normal Monster. If it battles a monster with a higher Level, the equipped monster gains 500 ATK x the difference in Levels, during that damage calculation only. When this card is sent to the GY: You can place it on top of your Deck.
